    <!-- About Screen -->
    <string name="about_title">About Project Huerto</string>
    <string name="about_main_desc">This application is designed to be your ideal companion in managing your ecological and sustainable garden. Here you will find everything you need to plan, record, and learn.</string>
    <string name="about_bancales_title">My Garden Beds</string>
    <string name="about_bancales_desc">It is the heart of your garden. Here you can create and customize your garden beds (the growing areas). Define their dimensions and add the crops you plan to plant. Visualize your garden in a graphic and organized way.</string>
    <string name="about_diario_title">Gardening Log</string>
    <string name="about_diario_desc">Your personal log. Every time you perform an important action such as watering, sowing, or harvesting in one of your beds, the event will be automatically recorded in this section, with the exact date and time. This way, you won\'t lose any detail of your crops\' progress!</string>
    <string name="about_plagas_title">Pest Guide</string>
    <string name="about_plagas_desc">An informative section to help you identify and combat the most common pests ecologically. Learn to recognize symptoms and apply organic treatments to keep your garden healthy.</string>
    <string name="about_consejos_title">Tips</string>
    <string name="about_consejos_desc">Here you will find recommendations and best practices to get the most out of your garden. From sowing techniques to how to improve soil quality, this section will guide you every step of the way.</string>
